00:10:08.029 --> 00:10:22.064
It's not like reading a passage of scripture one time and bypassing it. Faith cometh by hearing and hearing by the Word of God.

00:10:22.065 --> 00:10:32.443
If ye abide in Me and My words remain in you, you shall ask what you will and it shall be done.

00:10:32.444 --> 00:10:45.564
