00:10:52.950 --> 00:11:07.297
If your prayers aren't getting answered and you don't see results, check your Word level. Check what you're meditating on.

00:11:07.298 --> 00:11:22.241
The more you meditate on the Word and renew your mind, the more that Word gets down inside of you and becomes a rhema word, not just reading scripture.

00:11:22.242 --> 00:11:40.559
I did that, and the Lord asked me, 'Now, what did you learn?'I said, 'I don't know if I learned anything.'He said, 'Then what good did it do you?'You have to understand the Word; you shall know the truth, and the truth will set you free.

00:11:40.560 --> 00:11:45.093
