I lift them up and ask for mercy. I pray over Donald Trump, Father, for a radical conversion.

00:49:21.700 --> 00:49:45.723
I'm looking for a president who is on fire for Jesus, who prays in tongues in the White House and confesses that Jesus Christ is Lord behind the podium.

00:49:45.724 --> 00:50:22.550
We need someone with a backbone like a crowbar—boldness in faith and in what we stand for. We give You glory, honor, and praise for it in Jesus'name.

00:50:22.552 --> 00:50:33.462
Now, for all of you who say, 'What are you going to pray next?'I'm going to pray in tongues.

00:50:33.463 --> 00:51:15.804
That's the language of the Spirit, like in Acts chapter 2. I'm going to pray in the spirit right now and see if the Lord wants to show me anything.

00:51:15.805 --> 00:51:28.244
Father, I yield my body and spirit to You, that You pray through me in tongues.

00:51:28.245 --> 00:59:45.919
Show me the direction of the Father's heart today. There are some of you out there who are believing for the baptism right now.

00:59:45.920 --> 00:59:56.173
Receive the baptism of the Holy Spirit right now in the name of Jesus.

00:59:56.175 --> 01:00:43.519
Now begin to speak with other tongues; He's not going to move your tongue for you, you've got to move your tongue.

01:00:43.520 --> 01:02:24.798
There's a great revival coming for Africa. I see it. Hallelujah.

01:02:24.799 --> 01:04:01.576
Oh Lord, we thank You for a fresh touch. I receive it now in Jesus'name. Holy Spirit, You are welcome in this place.

01:04:01.577 --> 01:04:30.590
Lord said to me, 'I want my people to have some joy in this journey.'Be happy and full of His joy, for in His presence there is fullness of joy.

01:04:30.591 --> 01:05:15.364
In the days ahead, there shouldn't be dread. He wants to fill you with joy.

01:05:15.365 --> 01:05:59.683
Put a song in your heart, singing and making melody unto the Lord with psalms and hymns.

01:05:59.684 --> 01:06:08.850
All the lies told in your ears telling you God doesn't love you are lies.

01:06:08.851 --> 01:06:26.118
I hear fresh revelation of the love of God on you today, for God is love.

01:06:26.119 --> 01:07:22.957
Thank You for Your love for Your church and Your children. Come unto Me, and I will give you rest.

01:07:22.958 --> 01:07:41.101
His yoke is easy and His burden is light. Thank You, Father, for the healing and restoration of minds.

01:07:41.102 --> 01:09:26.678
We worship You today. The glory of the Lord is here. Jesus—there's just something about Your name. Savior, Jesus, like a fragrance after the rain.

01:09:26.679 --> 01:11:17.358
Let all heaven and earth proclaim: kings and kingdoms will all pass away, but there's something about Your name.

01:11:17.359 --> 01:11:29.194
In this atmosphere, you can get anything—healing or deliverance. Reach up and just grab a hold of it by faith.

01:11:29.195 --> 01:12:21.914
Say, 'I receive it now.'I can sense His mighty presence in the very atmosphere.

01:12:21.915 --> 01:14:29.347
Reach out and say, 'It's mine, I take it now.'You just have to receive it.

01:14:29.348 --> 01:14:36.669
I get lost in His presence. This is why people ask how long I pray.

01:14:36.670 --> 01:14:50.405
It's just a lifestyle; you don't time God. You don't talk to the King that way.

01:14:50.406 --> 01:15:24.979
You flow until He says you're released. Most people have no idea what a relationship is like.

01:15:24.980 --> 01:15:31.472
You don't tell your spouse you're only going to talk for 15 minutes and then be done.

01:15:31.473 --> 01:15:42.234
A relationship is not a time clock. It's real. That's where you see demonstrations and manifestations.

01:15:42.235 --> 01:16:18.099
He inhabits the praises of His people. It's a river; you don't control a river.

01:16:18.100 --> 01:16:49.310
The river is always flowing. The Holy Spirit is always flowing; He's not stagnant.

01:16:49.311 --> 01:17:01.359
I think that's good for today. I appreciate every one of you who joined me.

01:17:01.360 --> 01:17:13.621
I feel like we got some stuff accomplished today. Tomorrow we'll do it again.

01:17:13.622 --> 01:17:38.066
I will set time aside to pray with you all for the election, the storms, and that Jesus becomes real to the people.

01:17:38.067 --> 01:17:44.908
If you're new here, please like my video and subscribe. It helps with the algorithm.

01:17:44.909 --> 01:18:07.522
Comment something nice down below. Click the notification bell.

01:18:07.523 --> 01:18:47.209
God bless every single one of you. Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart. Jesus loves you so much. Have a wonderful day full of joy.

01:18:47.210 --> 01:18:54.681
May the Lord bless you and keep you, may His face shine upon you, and give you peace. Goodbye.

